

一、配置
main.py
数据库的IP、用户名、密码
MYSQL_HOST = 'xxxxxx'
MYSQL_USERNAME = 'xxxxxx'
MYSQL_PASSWORD = 'xxxxxx'

ModeBus服务器的信息
MODBUS_TCP_SERVER = 'xxxxxx'
MODBUS_TCP_PORT = 'xxxxxx'

二、运行
docker开机期自动 Web、Grafana


三、data_format 参数格式详情：
    Format	c Type	Python	Note
    x	pad byte	no value
    c	char	string of length 1
    b	signedchar	integer
    B	unsignedchar	integer
    ?	_Bool	bool	(1)
    h	short	integer
    H	unsignedshort	integer
    i	int	integer
    I	unsignedint	integer or long
    l	long	integer
    L	unsignedlong	long
    q	longlong	long	(2)
    Q	unsignedlonglong	long	(2)
    f	float	float
    d	double	float
    s	char[]	string
    p	char[]	string
    P	void*	long

    =	native	standard
    <	little-endian	standard
    >	big-endian	standard
    !	network (= big-endian)	standard